#

Baked Cod with Lemon and Dill

30 min
$15
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Low-CarbGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

HealthyQuickEasy

Description

A light and flavorful dish featuring tender baked cod, brightened with fresh lemon and aromatic dill.

Ingredients

  • cod fillets: 4 pieces
  • lemon: 1, sliced
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
